You get to choose a number...

00:17:17.021 --> 00:17:21.024
You reach various kinds of pocket, let's say.

00:17:27.098 --> 00:17:32.040
Going back to this concept of packages,

00:17:33.097 --> 00:17:38.005
it's what I'm going to talk about in the end, now that we 
are in ... this here is retail

00:17:38.009 --> 00:17:47.074
It´s retail you know, take three, pay two, 
is a way for you to increase your average ticket

00:17:47.074 --> 00:17:54.084
and reach more people who eventually 
want to buy the...

00:17:54.084 --> 00:18:01.093
They want to buy the full content, 
but they have doubts because of the price.

00:18:07.046 --> 00:18:14.043
Users are the best prospects, it´s much easier, 
it´s also known retail technique.

00:18:14.043 --> 00:18:20.003
It´s way easier to sell to whom 
already bought from you,

00:18:20.003 --> 00:18:22.010
than to somebody that doesn´t know your product.

00:18:22.010 --> 00:18:25.014
This is easy, obviously.

00:18:25.014 --> 00:18:33.057
And you have to take advantage of this 
characteristic of people, right?

00:18:33.057 --> 00:18:37.081
They feel confident, they may have already bought it, 
they already know what it is, and they'll want to buy it again.

00:18:41.086 --> 00:18:42.094
Sales

00:18:42.094 --> 00:18:45.043
Once more, retail.

00:18:47.099 --> 00:18:51.008
You have to take advantage of it in all the ways, 
you have to prepare for it.

00:18:51.008 --> 00:18:55.070
There are few times a year with this opportunity,

00:18:55.070 --> 00:19:00.056
that you can grow your revenue, 
give peaks of three to five times,

00:19:00.056 --> 00:19:06.025
and after, to even have a positive residual 
for some time.

00:19:06.025 --> 00:19:13.003
So, sales is the time to work and 
try to sell more.

00:19:16.081 --> 00:19:18.077
Retail again.

00:19:18.077 --> 00:19:21.037
All the sales techniques 
that you can possibly know.

