Splash discount.

00:19:42.096 --> 00:19:50.029
All this type, this tool that comes 
from the retail and sales.

00:19:50.079 --> 00:19:54.035
You have to take advantage in the time of 
making your sales screen.

00:19:57.022 --> 00:20:04.044
Here is perhaps the tip the most 
difficult to achieve,

00:20:04.044 --> 00:20:11.020
which is to find certain points of your app 
that with small changes,

00:20:11.020 --> 00:20:15.095
you will achieve a great increase 
in engagement or sales.

00:20:16.002 --> 00:20:18.076
A classic example of this is Facebook and LinkedIn,

00:20:18.076 --> 00:20:24.037
who discovered that, from X numbers of 
users that the person puts on the network,

00:20:24.037 --> 00:20:26.083
the network will continue.

00:20:26.083 --> 00:20:31.004
Here you can think in points like

00:20:31.004 --> 00:20:39.004
Oh, OK. I´ve already sold a video to this person, 
if I offer him the next collection, maybe he will buy.

00:20:39.004 --> 00:20:46.037
Or, if this person watched more than five videos, 
it´s very likely that this person wants to buy.

00:20:46.037 --> 00:20:54.008
If they have gone through five phases of the game, is very 
likely that they want to buy the other.

00:20:54.008 --> 00:20:55.020
And so on.

